*************************Selenium Class 06**********************************

************ Handling Alerts in Selenium ****************
What is an alert?
Alert is the popup message that you get on your application.
Alert takes the focus of our main screen/page.
We cannot proceed until we can handle this alert.

Types of Alerts:
1.WebBased Alerts/html Alerts: We can simply inspect them, deal with them in a regular way.
2.javascript alerts: We can handle these alerts by using Alert interface in Selenium.
3.Window-based alert: We cannot handle them in Selenium.


